{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/delay"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"delay","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh17TransitionMessageP5delays5UInt8VSgvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","required":true},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A base protocol for a message that can initiate a non-immediate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state transition."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"TransitionMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TransitionMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"TransitionMessage"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/transitionTime":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/transitiontime","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Transition Time field identifies the time that an Element will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"take to transition to the target state from the present state."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transitionTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TransitionTime","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh14TransitionTimeV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"transitionTime"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/delay":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/delay","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"title":"delay"}}}